curam.util.ctm.bom.businessobjectinformation

Interface BusinessObjectInformation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BusinessObjectInformationImpl

    public interface BusinessObjectInformation
extends java.io.Serializable
    Defines a business object information object, used by business object modules to specify the details of the business object instance of a particular type.
    Since:
    6.0
